getBuildVariables

public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getBuildVariables()
Description copied from class: AbstractBuild
Provides additional variables and their values to Builders.

This mechanism is used by MatrixConfiguration to pass the configuration values to the current build. It is up to Builders to decide whether it wants to recognize the values or how to use them. ugly ugly hack.
